title: [Mercantyler's Debt Collection]
description: The bright moonlight spilling through the south facing window makes this cluttered office appear less crowded.  Shelves filled with dust-covered ledgers cover the walls.  A large oak desk sits in the center of the room.  A thick ledger takes up most of the desk space, along with several quills and bottles of red and black ink.
